libdbi-drivers (Drivers for the Database Independent Abstraction Layer)

libdbi implements a database-independent abstraction layer in C, 
similar to the DBI/DBD layer in Perl. Writing one generic set of 
code, programmers can leverage the power of multiple databases and 
multiple simultaneous database connections by using this framework.

depends on libdbi

if you want the PostgreSQL integration, you must first have postgresql 
installed, and then pass the PGSQL=true flag.
postgresql is available at SlackBuilds.org

